# 1. How the layers should talk

## Control Layer ↔ Memory Management

The control layer needs memory for:

| Control Component | Memory Need                                                                        |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Planner           | Retrieve user/project context, SOPs, past workflows, templates, semantic knowledge |
| Planner           | Store generated plans and plan versions                                            |
| Orchestrator      | Read execution context and task history                                            |
| Orchestrator      | Write task state, checkpoints, retries, tool outputs                               |
| Supervisor        | Read checkpoints, failure history, risk context, previous escalation decisions     |
