## 5.1 Orchestrator → Governance before dispatch

Before the Dispatcher calls an agent, MCP tool, API, database, or LLM, it must call Governance.

```text
Ready TaskNode
   ↓
Task Scheduler
   ↓
Dispatcher
   ↓
Governance: authorize_tool_call()
   ↓
Allowed? execute
Approval required? pause
Denied? supervisor decision
