# 6. Supervisor → Memory and Governance

Supervisor makes runtime decisions.

It needs Memory to know:

```text
What happened?
How many retries happened?
Was this failure seen before?
What did the previous checkpoint say?
What is the current plan state?
What risk level was assigned?
```

It needs Governance to decide:

```text
Can execution continue?
Should it retry?
Should it re-plan?
Should it escalate?
Should it stop?
```

