# 4. `TaskNode`

## Purpose

This is the smallest executable unit inside the plan.

It is used by both:

```text
Planner → to define the task
Orchestrator → to execute the task
Supervisor → to inspect task state/failure
Governance → to evaluate task/tool risk
```

## Should contain

| Field               | Meaning                                         |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| `task_id`           | Unique task ID                                  |
| `name`              | Human-readable task name                        |
| `description`       | What the task does                              |
| `task_type`         | retrieval/analysis/generation/action/validation |
| `agent_required`    | Whether an agent is needed                      |
| `tool`              | Tool/API/agent to call                          |
| `dependencies`      | Previous tasks required                         |
| `input_refs`        | Memory/artifact references                      |
| `output_contract`   | Expected output structure                       |
| `timeout_seconds`   | Execution timeout                               |
| `retry_policy`      | Retry count/backoff                             |
| `risk_level`        | Low/medium/high/restricted                      |
| `approval_required` | Whether human approval is needed                |
| `evidence_required` | Evidence needed for audit/supervision           |
| `fallback_strategy` | Retry/replan/escalate/skip                      |
| `status`            | pending/running/succeeded/failed/etc.           |

## Example

```json
{
  "task_id": "task-02",
  "name": "Analyze failure patterns",
  "description": "Analyze failed invoice records and identify common reconciliation failure causes.",
  "task_type": "analysis",
  "agent_required": true,
  "agent_type": "analysis_agent",
  "tool": {
    "tool_name": "llm_analysis_tool",
    "tool_type": "llm",
    "requires_external_call": false
  },
  "dependencies": ["task-01"],
  "input_refs": [
    {
      "source_task_id": "task-01",
      "artifact_ref": "artifact-invoice-records-001"
    }
  ],
  "output_contract": {
    "type": "failure_pattern_summary",
    "required_fields": ["top_failure_reasons", "confidence", "evidence"]
  },
  "timeout_seconds": 120,
  "retry_policy": {
    "max_retries": 2,
    "backoff_strategy": "exponential"
  },
  "risk_level": "medium",
  "approval_required": true,
  "evidence_required": true,
  "fallback_strategy": "replan_on_failure",
  "status": "pending"
}
```

