# 7. `ReplanRequest`

## Purpose

This is emitted by **Supervisor → Planner**.

It tells the Planner:

```text
The current plan cannot continue safely/effectively.
Create a revised plan using current state, failure reason, and constraints.
```

## Should contain

| Field                     | Meaning                                               |
| ------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| `replan_request_id`       | Unique replan request                                 |
| `run_id`                  | Current run                                           |
| `old_plan_id`             | Existing plan                                         |
| `old_plan_version`        | Existing version                                      |
| `trigger_reason`          | Why replan is needed                                  |
| `failed_task_id`          | Task that caused replan                               |
| `current_state_refs`      | Checkpoint/run state refs                             |
| `partial_outputs`         | Outputs that can be reused                            |
| `constraints_to_preserve` | Budget, policy, approvals, deadlines                  |
| `policy_constraints`      | Governance constraints                                |
| `memory_refs`             | Relevant memory/history                               |
| `requested_change_type`   | Replace task / add task / change tool / simplify plan |
| `deadline`                | Optional                                              |
| `requested_by`            | Supervisor/service                                    |

## Example

```json
{
  "contract_version": "1.0.0",
  "replan_request_id": "replan-001",
  "correlation_id": "corr-123",
  "run_id": "run-001",
  "old_plan_id": "plan-001",
  "old_plan_version": 1,
  "trigger_reason": "Repeated tool timeout",
  "failed_task_id": "task-02",
  "trigger_checkpoint_id": "chk-001",
  "supervisor_decision_ref": "sup-dec-002",
  "current_state_refs": ["chk-001", "run-state-001"],
  "partial_outputs": [
    {
      "task_id": "task-01",
      "output_ref": "artifact-invoice-records-001",
      "reuse_allowed": true
    }
  ],
  "constraints_to_preserve": {
    "max_cost_usd_remaining": 1.2,
    "data_classification": "confidential",
    "allowed_tools": ["sap_invoice_api", "local_llm_analysis_tool"]
  },
  "policy_constraints": {
    "external_llm_blocked": true,
    "human_approval_required_for_report_send": true
  },
  "requested_change_type": "replace_failed_tool",
  "requested_by": "supervisor"
}
```

