# 11. How the contracts connect

```text
RequestEnvelope
      ↓
Planner
      ↓
ExecutionPlan
      ↓
TaskNode[]
      ↓
Orchestrator
      ↓
StateCheckpoint
      ↓
Supervisor
      ↓
SupervisorDecision
      ↓
Retry / Continue / Replan / Escalate / Stop
      ↓
ReplanRequest, if needed
      ↓
Planner creates new ExecutionPlan version
```

Parallel contracts:

```text
Governance → PolicyDecision
Memory     → MemoryRecord
```

These two are used throughout the full flow.

