# 13. Final summary

The contracts will contain:

```text
1. Identity fields
   request_id, plan_id, task_id, run_id, checkpoint_id

2. Traceability fields
   correlation_id, timestamp, source_component, trace_context

3. Governance fields
   risk_level, data_classification, policy_decision_ref, approval_required

4. Runtime fields
   status, attempt, timeout, retry_policy, metrics

5. Memory fields
   memory_refs, artifact_refs, content_summary, run history references

6. Execution fields
   tool, agent, dependencies, input_refs, output_contract

7. Decision fields
   decision_type, reason_codes, next_action, escalation/replan flags
```

